<title>String Extension</title>
<indexterm><primary>String Extension</primary></indexterm>

<para>This package is a <link linkend="_namespace_twig">Twig</link> extension that provides integration with the Symfony String component.</para>

<para>It provides a <link xlink:href="https://twig.symfony.com/u"><computeroutput>u</computeroutput></link> filter that wraps a text in a <computeroutput>UnicodeString</computeroutput> object to give access to <link xlink:href="https://symfony.com/doc/current/components/string.html">methods of the class</link>.</para>

<para>It also provides a <link xlink:href="https://twig.symfony.com/slug"><computeroutput>slug</computeroutput></link> filter which is simply a wrapper for the <link xlink:href="https://symfony.com/doc/current/components/string.html#slugger"><computeroutput>AsciiSlugger</computeroutput></link>&apos;s <computeroutput>slug</computeroutput> method. </para>
</section>
